  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE \"MISSISSIPPI SOCIAL MEDIA TAX ACT\"; TO LEVY A TAX ON SOCIAL MEDIA PLATFORMS THAT FURNISH SERVICES TO USERS IN MISSISSIPPI; TO PROVIDE FOR THE RATE OF THE TAX; TO CREATE THE \"SOCIAL MEDIA PLATFORM INFRASTRUCTURE FUND\" AS A SPECIAL FUND IN THE STATE TREASURY; TO PROVIDE THE PURPOSES FOR WHICH MONIES IN THE FUND MAY BE USED; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
